1. *Upozorio* je kolege na mogući rizik. (He warned his colleagues about a possible risk.)
2. Oni su *upozorili* na nedostatak vode u gradu. (They pointed out the lack of water in the city.)
3. Nisam želeo da te *upozorim* jer ne želim da se mešam. (I didn't want to warn you because I don't want to interfere.)
4. Policajac je *upozorio* vozača da ne parkira na tom mestu. (The police officer warned the driver not to park in that spot.)
5. Nekoliko znakova *upozorava* na opasnost. (Several signs warn of danger.)
6. Njegov prijatelj ga je *upozorio* na potencijalne probleme. (His friend warned him about potential problems.)
7. Molim vas, *upozorite* me ako grešim. (Please warn me if I'm wrong.)
8. *Upozorenje* je bilo jasno i glasno. (The warning was clear and loud.)
9. Ovaj proizvod ima *upozorenje* na ambalaži. (This product has a warning on the packaging.)
10. Ako se *upozorenje* ignorira, mogu se javiti ozbiljne posledice. (If the warning is ignored, serious consequences can occur.)